<br>
&quot;Second-Generation Diet Members and Democracy in Japan: Hereditary Seats&quot;, by Michihiro Ishibashi and Steven R. Reed, in Asian Survey, Vol. 32, No. 4. Apr., 1992.<br>
<br>
Focusing on koenkai selectorates and the development of an &quot;elite cooptative model of democracy&quot; in Japan...<br>
<br>
Maybe part of what you're talking about?<br>
